%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BA%B7ng-T%E1%BB%AB-C%C3%A1n/poem-TMDCykIDLkn2ovF5EJROGQ">Tặng Từ Cán - 贈徐幹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-k%C3%BD-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-gi%C3%A1m-h%E1%BB%93-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-KlEQuifk8GeYdPwc84ehyw">Thu nhật ký đề Trịnh giám hồ thượng đình kỳ 1 - 秋日寄題鄭監湖上亭其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%97i/Tu%E1%BA%BF-m%E1%BB%99-Ph%C3%BAc-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95/poem-0ZTYkvhun1R1q8E-tyimOw">Tuế mộ Phúc Xương hoài cổ - 歲暮福昌懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%97i/author-5d8o2S_RIMOZD_yipGScpw">Trương Lỗi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/V%C4%83n-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-Re9QQHnBzA1D-k6ABbDqAg">Văn địch - 聞笛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/author-ZK21rLayK3mmuHkvR5sQcg">Triệu Hỗ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
